data.description: Very well maintained, custom built beautiful home surrounded by 5.93 acres of wooded privacy that borders the National Forest. Just a short scenic drive to beautiful downtown Clayton and only 18 miles to Highlands, NC with upscale shops and dining. Along with a great house and beautiful private property is a 24x48 covered shelter with full utilities and a storage room that is stubbed for a bathroom. The perfect place for your RV! Continue up the paved driveway to the home and enter through the custom front door to an inviting 2 story foyer. Enjoy large windows for great natural light and cozy up to the stacked stone fireplace on those cool evenings in the family room. Beyond the family room is the recently remodeled kitchen with beautiful cabinets, countertops, stainless steel farmhouse sink and appliances, and a dedicated pantry! Enjoy your meals in the separate large dining room adjoining the kitchen. The master suite (bedroom, sitting room, laundry room, walk in closet, and master bathroom) and a half bath conclude the main level. Upstairs you will find two rooms and a full bath. The basement is completely finished with a mini kitchen, specific laundry hookup, living room with fireplace, 3 rooms and 2 full baths. Plans for adding a full kitchen in basement are available upon request. This property would be perfect for a large family or for someone needing a completely separate space for guests. This is a RARE find! Schedule a showing to see for yourself!
